TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
No, that's just a bowl of mud.

Waiter, there's a heart in my soup!

I'm sorry, we ran out of kidneys

Waiter! There's a brain in my soup!

BBBBWWWWWRRRRAAAIIIIIINNNNNZZZZZZ!

Waiter, there's a live chicken in my soup!

Well... it is a chicken noodle soup...

Waiter, there's a Velvet Remedy in my soup!

Why are you in the soup?

Waiter, there's a robot in my soup! It looks like it's on a quest of some sort.

Yes. It looks like Joseph Stali- uhh i mean MARIO! Yeah, Mario.

Waiter, there's a communist in my soup!

No, that's a TF2 Engineer upgrading something. He's using a hammer for it, though.

Waiter, there's a kraken in my soup!

I thought Squad dealt with that in the 0.17 update!

Waiter, there's a Soviet Union in my soup!

Well it's dissolving.

Waiter, there's russian space geckos in my soup!

You should stop chasing reentering objects.

Waiter, there is a goldcrest in my soup!

Indeed, sir. I have utterly no idea whatsoever what a goldcrest is.

Waiter, there's nothing in my soup! This place is really clean, thanks! (-WAITER PROMOTED-)

Well, we don't call it 'Youdidn'torderanythinginourcleanrestaraunt' for nothing.

Waiter, there's a magical horse with a HORN in my cold water that's not even soup!

Let that annoying little thing freeze in that cold water.

Waiter, there's a water in my waiter!

*There is a note on that table that reads "Of course, i am a water balloon."*

Waiter, there's a Grox soldier in my soup!

Naw, they only got spaceships, man. That's a borg soldier.

Waiter, there's a disasteroid in my space rations! It's on an intersect trajectory at 0.01 m/s upon arrival and is going to knock the space rations off the table!

0.01 M/S?!?!?! THAT'S LIGHTING FAST! Call the navy, we have to destroy it quick!

Waiter, there's a Barrack Obama in my soup!

That's just a baby of a person who was jealous of Barack Obama..

Waiter, there's air in my soup!

Is it toxic air? I think it is. *Smashes gas mask into person's face for eternity*

Waiter, there's *CENSORED BY THE NSA* in my soup!

Well, it's *CENSORED BY THE KGB*

Waiter, there's a docking port in my soup!

If you dock your mouth with it it'll transfer the soup into your stomach.

WAITER!! There's a homeless man in my soup! Why isn't he drinking it?

because this is a soup kitchen, and that's HIS soup. I repeat HIS soup

Waiter, why is moist underwear in my soup?

You ordered the underwear soup sir, it was an odd request but we got you what you wanted.

Waiter, there's a battle of Trafalgar happening in my soup

really? because I thought the battle off samar soup was what you ordered

waiter, why is their a ship transporting ships transporting ships in my soup?

Because your fractal souffle just collapsed Sir. I apologize.

Waiter, why is there irony in my soup?

Why don't you go ask the chef, hmm?

Waiter!!! There's a space rations block in my soup!
